title: Diamond Mid looking for team (Plat+)
body:
Hey im a 16 Diamond, challenger in ranked 5s last season. I can do any Voice Com. I main mid: Zed, Oriana, Twisted Fate, Ryze, Varus... Hit me up with a high elo Team. Please dont waist your time if players are below plat :)
PS i can name change anytime

replies.body: add 'dule' ingame, he might have what you are looking for
